  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the clay pot to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Slice the baguette in half lengthwise and place it in the clay pot.",
    "Brush the baguette with olive oil and season with salt, pepper, and a sprinkle of spinach.",
    "Place the sliced turkey breast, red onion, avocado, cheddar cheese, lettuce, and tomato on one half of the baguette.",
    "Spread a thin layer of mayonnaise on the other half of the baguette.",
    "Place the two halves together to form a sandwich.",
    "Cook for 10 minutes or until the bread is toasted and the cheese is melted.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh parsley and serve hot.",
    "Let the sandwich rest for 2-3 minutes before slicing.",
    "Slice the sandwich in half and serve immediately."
  ],
